	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Montreal</placeName> <date>3d Decr&#47;62</date></p>
				<p>The <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philada</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Enclosed I forward<lb/> you&#44; as per request&#44; the resolutions<lb/> passed here in honor of <persName>Lady<lb/> Montefiore&#39;s</persName> memory.  I trust<lb/> you will deem our proceedings of<lb/> sufficient importance<lb/> to insert them in the &#8220;Occident.&#8221;<lb/>  They will no doubt reach you in<lb/> time for the next &#40;<date>Decr</date>&#41; number.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">My people lately presented<lb/> me &#40;for the third time&#41; with a<lb/> very liberal testimonial<lb/> accompanied by an address</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>I mail you with this a paper<lb/> containing the proceedings.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">It is long since I have<lb/> had the pleasure of receiving<lb/> a line from you.  Though I<lb/> do not publish&#44; like you&#44;<lb/> I assure you my time is so<lb/> taken up that I really cannot<lb/> find leisure for correspondence.<lb/>  Perhaps in time this may change.<lb/>  You will scarcely believe I have<lb/> not had time yet to complete<lb/>&#8212;altho&#39; I have nearly done so&#8212;<lb/> the biographical sketch I commenced<lb/> of my late father <add>Hebrew</add>&#8212;but the</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p>claims of my avocations are<lb/> pressing&#44;&#8212;you do not know<lb/> how many extra dollars&#8212;good<lb/> Canadian dollars and none of<lb/> your yankee shinplasters&#8212;it<lb/> requires to provide for all the<lb/> wants of a little family&#8212;but<lb/> I can assure you it makes a<lb/> tight squeeze on the house of<lb/> a <persName>Fortunatus</persName>.  So I have to devote<lb/> myself to that which brings a<lb/> more immediate return.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I will endeavor to write<lb/> you again soon&#44; as I must<lb/> go out now &#8220;on duty.&#8221;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Hoping you are quite well</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I remain yours faithfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">Abraham de Sola</persName></p>
			
